Achievements.Name: Stick it to McQueen
Achievements.Description: Beat the three Radiator Springs road races and the Relay Race, then place in the first Stadium Race

Achievements.Name: Rust Bust
Achievements.Description: Qualify in the first three Rustbucket Series races, then win the final

Achievements.Name: Golden Gas Can
Achievements.Description: Win each of the nine levels of Fillmore's Fuel Frenzy

Achievements.Name: Frank Slash
Achievements.Description: Tip all tractors before the time limit in each of the six levels of Tractor Tipping

Achievements.Name: High Draulics
Achievements.Description: Score well playing along with each of the seven songs in Ramone's Rhythmic Rumble

Achievements.Name: Ghost Light
Achievements.Description: Scare Mater home in each of the seven Ghosting Mater levels

Achievements.Name: James P. Sullivan Cup
Achievements.Description: Qualify in the first two Waypoint Race Series races, then finish in the top three of the final

Achievements.Name: Race 'n' Chase Victor
Achievements.Description: Tag your opponent then zoom to your goal without being tagged in all nine Race 'n' Chase levels

Achievements.Name: Unlock Tailfin Pass
Achievements.Description: Beat the three Ornament Valley road races and the Relay Race, then place in the second Stadium race

Achievements.Name: Find all Paintjobs
Achievements.Description: Find all 8 new paintjobs for Lightning McQueen

Achievements.Name: Find all wheel sets
Achievements.Description: Find all 8 new wheel sets for Lightning McQueen

Achievements.Name: Build Monster McQueen
Achievements.Description: Find two monster truck pieces, plus a new horn, so Luigi can build Monster McQueen

Achievements.Name: Build Monster Mater
Achievements.Description: Find six monster truck parts in Radiator Springs so Luigi can build Monster Mater

Achievements.Name: Win all Stadium Races
Achievements.Description: Finish first in all four races conducted in Lightning McQueen's new Racing Stadium

Achievements.Name: Win all Road Races
Achievements.Description: Radiator Springs, Ornament Valley, and Tailfin Pass -- win all three races in each area

Achievements.Name: Beat the game!
Achievements.Description: Collect every Bolt Banner and earn every sticker in the game
